text: Afeez Oyetoro born on August 20, 1963, is a Nigerian Actor, comedian known as "Saka" ==Early life and education== Afeez Oyetoro was born on the 20th of August, 1963, in Iseyin Local Government Area of Oyo State southwestern Nigeria. Finished from Obafemi Awolowo University (OAU) where he got his Bachelor's degree in Art, later went to the University of Ibadan (UI) for his master's degree in Theatre Art. Saka is now a doctorate degree holder from the University of Ibadan, Ibadan in Oyo State.
